# vhs script for the hero GIF (requires a prepared demo-acme scope + claude auth)
Output demo/hero.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1100
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Type "grandma demo-acme"
Enter
Sleep 6s
Type "we use pnpm here, never yarn. and never push to main directly."
Enter
Sleep 12s
Ctrl+D
Sleep 2s
Type "grandma demo-acme"
Enter
Sleep 6s
Type "set up the new billing service"
Enter
Sleep 15s
